OL,3,CLondon Fire Brigade says risk of
OL,4,Cunsafe buildings is not going away
OL,6,FMembers of the London Fire Brigade
OL,7,F(LFB) have been speaking to the London
OL,8,FAssembly following the publication of
OL,9,Fthe final phase of the Grenfell Tower
OL,10,FInquiry.
OL,12,FThe Grenfell Tower Inquiry Phase 2
OL,13,Freport showed 'systematic dishonesty'
OL,14,Fcontributed to the deaths of 72 people
OL,15,Fon 14 June 2017.
OL,17,FThe report said LFB should have been
OL,18,Faware of the shortcomings of cladding,
OL,19,Fparticularly with regard to high rises
OL,20,Fafter the Lakanal House fire in 2009.
