OL,6,FIt also highlighted a chronic lack of
OL,7,Feffective leadership and issues with
OL,8,Ftraining control room staff.
OL,10,FThe London Assembly Fire Committee
OL,11,Fquestioned the Deputy Mayors
OL,12,Fresponsible for housing and the fire
OL,13,Fservice, along with senior
OL,14,Frepresentatives from the London Fire
OL,15,FBrigade (LFB), how they will respond
OL,16,Fto the Inquiry's findings and
OL,17,Frecommendations.
