OL,3,CLondon Fire Brigade says risk of
OL,4,Cunsafe buildings is not going away
OL,6,FFollowing from Phase One, the Brigade
OL,7,Fsay they 'accepted every
OL,8,Frecommendation' and 'completed every
OL,9,Frecommendation'.
OL,11,FToday, Andy Roe, Commissioner of LFB,
OL,12,Fcited Dagenham as an example of where
OL,13,Fthe service had improved after a "3.5
OL,14,Fmillion pound investment" into the
OL,15,Fforce's logistics.
OL,17,F"I need to be responsible and evidence
OL,18,Fthe outcome for communities when it
OL,19,Flands," said Commissioner Roe.
