OL,3,CLondon Fire Brigade says risk of
OL,4,Cunsafe buildings is not going away
OL,6,F"We've got a lot better...we see
OL,7,Fchallenge in ourselves."
OL,9,FThe commissioner went on to explain
OL,10,Fall 5000 firefighters have been
OL,11,Ftrained to respond differently which
OL,12,Fincludes taking early decisions and
OL,13,Fcommunicating continuously.
OL,15,FJonathan Smith, Deputy Commissioner
OL,16,Fand Operational Director for
OL,17,Fpreparedness and Response added: "If I
OL,18,Flook back to when I joined 25 years
OL,19,Fago, the job is almost unrecognisable."
