OL,6,FHe said it's important that the
OL,7,Ftraining provision is as agile as it
OL,8,Fcan be which is a "challenge for the
OL,9,Fsector".
OL,11,FHowever, the meeting then turned on to
OL,12,Fthe question of regulatory bodies to
OL,13,Fwhich Andy Roe described as "not good
OL,14,Fenough yet".
OL,16,F"As we have been saying for some time,
OL,17,Fthe regulation - whilst welcoming from
OL,18,Fphase one, (brings) some very
OL,19,Fimportant changes but they still don't
OL,20,Fhave enough teeth and they need better
OL,21,Falignment," he explained.
