OL,3,CLondon Fire Brigade says risk of
OL,4,Cunsafe buildings is not going away
OL,6,FAccording to the London Fire Brigade,
OL,7,Fthere are still 1307 unsafe buildings.
OL,9,FThe Deputy Commissioner, Charlie
OL,10,FPugsley, described a building that was
OL,11,Fjust below 50 metres high, with one
OL,12,Fstaircase and no evacuation lift.
OL,14,F"You have to go to the root of the
OL,15,Fproblem before you get to regulation,"
OL,16,Fsaid Commissioner Roe.
OL,18,FThere were suggestions discussed for
OL,19,Fhow to solve the problem, and one of
OL,20,Fthose was expropriation.
