OL,3,CLondon Fire Brigade says risk of
OL,4,Cunsafe buildings is not going away
OL,6,F"We have powers, the building safety
OL,7,Fgroups have powers, the secretary of
OL,8,Fstate has powers...we all need to be
OL,9,Fworking together in one system,"
OL,10,Fcontinued Commissioner Roe.
OL,12,F"The report is quite clear about that
OL,13,Fand we recognise a lot of what has
OL,14,Fbeen said there...all of this goes to
OL,15,Fan investment in skills, a moral
OL,16,Fapproach to the construction
OL,17,Fsector...I think the report is a
OL,18,Fwatershed moment to go back to what
OL,19,Fhas already been done with good intent
OL,20,Fand do better."
